      <title>由于中国需求疲软，资生堂面临最大幅度的目标价格下调</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/shiseido-faces-steepest-cut-in-target-price-on-weak-china-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国需求疲软导致日本化妆品公司资生堂下调盈利预期，导致该公司股价创下有记录以来最大年度跌幅，分析师大幅下调该公司的目标价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/shiseido-faces-steepest-cut-in-target-price-on-weak-china-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 02:33:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国恒大香港清盘听证会再次延期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-04/evergrande-winding-up-hearing-in-hk-adjourned-again-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港一家法院再次驳回了关于全球负债最重的房地产开发商中国恒大集团是否应该清盘的决定。诉讼程序已延期至 1 月 29 日。Lorretta Chen 在彭博电视台进行报道。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2023-12-04/evergrande-winding-up-hearing-in-hk-adjourned-again-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Dec 2023 02:28:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恒大清算听证会推迟，令贷款人感到惊讶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-04/evergrande-winding-up-hearing-in-hong-kong-adjourned-to-jan-29</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在香港法院再次驳回有关全球负债最重的房地产开发商是否应该清盘的决定后，中国恒大集团赢得了与债权人达成重组协议的喘息空间。]]></description>
